## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Resolution |
| --- | --- |
| **Sidecar Status Error** | Ensure Node.js is running. Check if `8765` is blocked by a firewall. |
| **Balance is 0** | Ensure you are on the correct network (Mainnet vs. Regtest). If using a WoS seed, ensure the wallet has been migrated to self-custody. |
| **Invoice Failing** | Check Sidecar logs for "Insufficient Liquidity." Spark L2 manages liquidity automatically, but large spikes can occasionally cause temporary delays. |